#~ msgstr "Dodaj do słownika"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Pressing this button adds the <guilabel>Unknown word </guilabel> to the "
#~ "checker's dictionary. This means that in the future the checker will "
#~ "always consider this word to be correctly spelled."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Naciśnięcie przycisku spowoduje dodanie <guilabel>nieznanego słowa</"
